search_results.title: Justin Gammella
search_results.snippet: Justin Gammella is a producer, topliner, and multi-instrumentalist based in Los Angeles. Justin's songwriting and production can be heard on records.

search_results.title: Justin Gammella - Band Member and songwriter
search_results.snippet: Classically trained composer, Singer/songwriter, and producer Justin Gammella has worked in nearly every spectrum of music.
